-- China’s Shanghai Composite Index Rises, Erasing Earlier Decline
-- B y   W e i y i   L i m
-- 2012-05-03T01:51:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-03/china-s-shanghai-composite-index-rises-erasing-earlier-decline.html
China’s stocks rose, erasing earlier
losses on speculation the central bank will ease monetary policy
to boost economic growth.  The Shanghai Composite Index gained 0.1 percent to 2,439.69
at 9:48 a.m. local time, wiping out a loss of as much
as 0.3 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
